{"id":29913,"date":"2024-01-11T18:47:00","date_gmt":"2022-01-11T13:17:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=29913"},"modified":"2024-03-18T06:43:49","modified_gmt":"2024-03-18T01:13:49","slug":"modern-staircase-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-staircase-design\/","title":{"rendered":"Spiral, Wooden Or Floating? Pick From These 10 Modern Staircase Design Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Take your home interiors to new heights of style with our modern staircase design ideas&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Staircases are the connectors of spaces. They bring different levels together, forming a continuity in your home\u2019s interiors. Staircases are also great elements for interior design. They are becoming the focal points of home interiors as they can accentuate the aesthetics of a place. This is why modern home designs, especially living room designs, revolve around the staircase. It becomes an obvious choice to invest in a modern staircase design while setting up your home. From materials to types of staircases, there is a whole new world of modern staircase designs for homes to redefine your space as you want. So, without delaying any further, let us jump into our modern staircase design gallery that can totally elevate your home interiors!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Wooden Staircase Designs Will Leave You Spellbound<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Spirals are in! They look attractive and add an architectural treat to interiors. This is why spiral staircases are a popular choice in modern staircase designs for homes. The spiral staircase here reveals a classic wooden stairs and wooden railing design. The staircase forms a convoluted spiral design that accentuates the room&#8217;s interiors. Besides, the spiral design also efficiently saves space, allowing you to take control of the entry and exit points of the staircase. Such modern spiral staircase design is ideal for urban living areas that have less space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190332\/modern-staircase-design-will-leave-you-spellbound.jpg\" alt=\"Modern staircase design will leave you spellbound which look attractive and add an architectural treat to interiors\" class=\"wp-image-29914\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190332\/modern-staircase-design-will-leave-you-spellbound.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190332\/modern-staircase-design-will-leave-you-spellbound-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190332\/modern-staircase-design-will-leave-you-spellbound-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190332\/modern-staircase-design-will-leave-you-spellbound-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Match wooden flooring with a modern wooden staircase<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Wooden Staircase Designs That Float<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Not a fan of bulky staircase designs? Why not choose a subtle and simple modern staircase design that fits into your type of home interiors? Compared to the conventional staircase designs, floating staircases are like a breath of fresh air. They are simple, minimalist and totally offbeat. Floating staircases do not have the supporting staircase structure \u2013 you can have a simple handrail structure, though. The floating treads of the staircase make the setup look light and airy, saving you a lot of space. Floating modern wooden staircase designs are also undeniably gorgeous. Moreover, the absence of the supporting structure makes this staircase design perfect for small homes that can use the extra space beneath the staircase.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190944\/modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-that-float.jpg\" alt=\"Modern staircase designs for homes that float\" class=\"wp-image-29915\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190944\/modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-that-float.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190944\/modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-that-float-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190944\/modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-that-float-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16190944\/modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-that-float-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Floating staircases are ideal for minimalist interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Natural And Sustainable Modern Staircase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Natural is the new lavish! As awareness towards an eco-conscious world rises, people are becoming inclined towards natural and sustainable living choices. And this echoes clearly in the interior design world, where both homeowners and designers are opting for natural materials and finishes. In terms of modern staircase design too, people are going all-natural. While cafes and restaurant designs are going with stone or bamboo staircase designs, in home interiors, there is a new wave of using the old-school marble and stone staircase designs. The natural materials bring an organic appeal and are also functionally sustainable.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191139\/a-natural-and-sustainable-modern-wooden-staircase-designs.jpg\" alt=\"A natural and sustainable modern wooden staircase designs to pair with marble flooring\" class=\"wp-image-29916\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191139\/a-natural-and-sustainable-modern-wooden-staircase-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191139\/a-natural-and-sustainable-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191139\/a-natural-and-sustainable-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191139\/a-natural-and-sustainable-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A staircase design to pair with marble flooring<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Paddle-Style Modern Wooden Staircase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wood is another natural wonder that we all love. And in staircase design, wood is forming a whole new level! The modern wooden staircase design here features an innovative design that reveals the intricacy of modern architecture. The wooden paddle staircase design reveals a free-flowing spiral structure with broad and creative stair treads that are simply stunning. The paddle stairs save space and add a glamorous appeal to the interiors. This type of staircase is ideal for small homes. You might want to avoid this type of staircase if you have small children around the house.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191407\/a-paddle-style-modern-curved-staircase-designs.jpg\" alt=\"A paddle-style modern curved staircase designs with a modern staircase for an earthy living room\" class=\"wp-image-29917\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191407\/a-paddle-style-modern-curved-staircase-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191407\/a-paddle-style-modern-curved-staircase-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191407\/a-paddle-style-modern-curved-staircase-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191407\/a-paddle-style-modern-curved-staircase-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern staircase for an earthy living room\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tornado Form Modern Spiral Staircase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn&#8217;t love a super stylish staircase design? This tornado form spiral staircase is a modern-day adventurous staircase design that will totally glam up your place. Elegantly wrapped in a white supporting structure, this modern spiral staircase design instantly increases the style quotient of home interiors. The spiral forms the shape of a tornado, creating a distinguished design for the interiors. This type of staircase is great for a spacious home with modern architectural designs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191636\/tornado-form-modern-staircase-design.jpg\" alt=\"Tornado form modern staircase design as convoluted spiral staircase design\" class=\"wp-image-29918\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191636\/tornado-form-modern-staircase-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191636\/tornado-form-modern-staircase-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191636\/tornado-form-modern-staircase-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191636\/tornado-form-modern-staircase-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A convoluted spiral staircase design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Minimalist Cantilever Modern Staircase Design&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another modern staircase design is this type of floating \u2013 aka cantilever staircase \u2013 that is simple, subtle and stunning. The sleek staircase design reveals a very effortless staircase design, ideal for modern homes with minimalist interior design. The stairs are comfortable and airy, allowing you to save a lot of space. These types of modern wooden staircase designs give you a lot of under the stairs space which is great for modern Indian apartments.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191830\/minimalist-cantilever-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes.jpg\" alt=\"Modern staircase designs for homes ideal for modern homes \" class=\"wp-image-29919\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191830\/minimalist-cantilever-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191830\/minimalist-cantilever-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191830\/minimalist-cantilever-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16191830\/minimalist-cantilever-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sleek modern wooden staircase design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Visually striking staircase designs that make your home beautiful\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/06164912\/visually-striking-staircase-designs-that-make-your-home-beautiful-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Whirlpool-Style Modern Staircase With Glass Railing Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your home&#8217;s staircase can be the most stunning design element in your place. Hence, it gives the greatest opportunity for you to analyse different types in our modern staircase design gallery and find something suitable for your place. If you have a minimalistic themed interior design for your place, go ahead with this type of spiral design. It exhibits an elegant sharp spiral that\u2019s wrapped in a clear glass panelling. This type of modern spiral staircase design is ideal for narrow spaces.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192049\/whirlpool-style-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-with-glass-railing-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Whirlpool-style modern wooden staircase designs with glass railing designs\" class=\"wp-image-29920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192049\/whirlpool-style-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-with-glass-railing-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192049\/whirlpool-style-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-with-glass-railing-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192049\/whirlpool-style-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-with-glass-railing-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192049\/whirlpool-style-modern-wooden-staircase-designs-with-glass-railing-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern staircase with a glass railing design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cool Modern Staircase Design With Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern homes require modern solutions! Today, space is the most crucial part of homes because let&#8217;s face it, urban apartments aren&#8217;t getting bigger! So, the ideal solution is to maximise storage in your house to have enough room for joy in your place. If you think that storage solutions are only limited to wardrobes and beds, check out this super cool modern staircase design with hidden storage. The stair treads are nothing but storage boxes that can store your books, soft toys and other things without taking any extra space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192220\/cool-modern-curved-staircase-designs-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Cool modern curved staircase designs with storage as A space-saving staircase design with storage\" class=\"wp-image-29921\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192220\/cool-modern-curved-staircase-designs-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192220\/cool-modern-curved-staircase-designs-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192220\/cool-modern-curved-staircase-designs-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192220\/cool-modern-curved-staircase-designs-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A space-saving staircase design with storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modular Space-Saving Modern Staircase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This one here is the perfect example of utilising space! The modern staircase design exhibits a narrow, sleek design that takes a lot less space than your regular standard staircases. The staircase is more of a straight ladder design that is ideal for a single person. You can have this type of staircase design for small apartments where you don&#8217;t have to make extra space for your staircase design.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192416\/modular-space-saving-modern-staircase-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modular space saving modern staircase design which is a perfect example of utilising space\" class=\"wp-image-29922\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192416\/modular-space-saving-modern-staircase-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192416\/modular-space-saving-modern-staircase-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192416\/modular-space-saving-modern-staircase-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192416\/modular-space-saving-modern-staircase-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sleek and minimalist modern staircase design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rustic Steel Modern Staircase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Steel staircase design may not be the most popular choice, especially for interiors. However, modern times require modern designs, which is why modern steel staircase designs for homes are the new way of innovating staircase designs. Even if not very popular in home interiors, steel staircase designs gain recognition, primarily because of their aesthetically pleasing looks and durability. Modern staircase designs are all about providing versatility with cost-effectiveness, which are the plus points of steel staircases. They also bring a rustic appeal to your house, giving a personality to the place.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192749\/rustic-steel-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes.jpg\" alt=\"Modern staircase designs for homes which is a new way of innovating staircase designs\" class=\"wp-image-29923\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192749\/rustic-steel-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192749\/rustic-steel-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192749\/rustic-steel-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16192749\/rustic-steel-modern-staircase-designs-for-homes-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A stunning modern staircase design in steel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here you are, this is our modern staircase design gallery with ten unique ideas that are surely going to elevate your home interiors. Besides, they are also going to help you save space and make more room in your home. So go on, take your place&#8217;s design to a whole new level with these modern staircase designs. If you need consultation for your new home&#8217;s interiors, write to us now!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about modern staircase designs, also explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/staircase-design-ideas-for-indian-homes\/\">staircase designs for indian homes<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.